Title : Memorial Private High School
Text : {{third-party|date=May 2014}}
'''Memorial Private High School''' ('''MPHS''') is a private 6-12 Christian school in the [[Memorial, Houston|Memorial]] area of [[Houston]], [[Texas]]. It opened in 2005.<ref>[http://www.memorialprivateschool.com/ Home]. Memorial Private High School. Retrieved on April 30, 2014. "14333 Fern Drive • Houston, TX 77079"</ref> It was established by Harry and Pam Camp, who respectively originated from the [[Sharpstown, Houston|Sharpstown]] and [[Spring Branch, Houston|Spring Branch]] communities.<ref>"[http://www.memorialprivateschool.com/about.html About]." Memorial Private High School. Retrieved on April 30, 2014. "14333 Fern Drive • Houston, TX 77079"</ref>

